          "oldLine": null,
          "newLine": 8
        },
        {
          "kind": "add",
          "text": "## Auth Flow",
          "oldLine": null,
          "newLine": 9
        },
        {
          "kind": "add",
          "text": "",
          "oldLine": null,
          "newLine": 10
        },
        {
          "kind": "add",
          "text": "1. `POST /api/auth/login` — returns `accessToken` (15 min) + `refreshToken` (7 days)",
          "oldLine": null,
          "newLine": 11
        },
        {
          "kind": "add",
          "text": "2. Client stores `refreshToken` in httpOnly cookie",
          "oldLine": null,
          "newLine": 12
        },
        {
          "kind": "add",
          "text": "3. On 401, client calls `POST /api/auth/refresh` to get new `accessToken`",
          "oldLine": null,
          "newLine": 13
        },
        {
          "kind": "add",
          "text": "4. `POST /api/auth/logout` revokes the `refreshToken`",
          "oldLine": null,
          "newLine": 14
        },
        {
          "kind": "add",
          "text": "",
          "oldLine": null,
          "newLine": 15
        },
        {
          "kind": "add",
          "text": "## Data Model",
